<br>
We are an Everquest guild on the Mithaniel Marr Server.  We are adults, or adult-seeming, mature children, who raid primarily on Eastern Standard Time.  We are people of the highest quality.  While some of us are not the most skilled players, personality is our first and foremost requirement, we are all at least ok.  Additionally, we are nice people.  We generally abide by the same unwritten rules that all other second tier guilds (Forsaken Realm thru Prime) seem to abide by.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">How often do you raid?</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
We will normally have events almost every day.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>How active must I be to be a member in good standing?</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
<br>
Not at all, you may choose to raid or not to raid on your whim.  All events are optional.  Of course, this will have bearing on how much raid loot you tend to receive when you do choose to raid and also may have bearing on whether you are assured a spot on the raid force.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">Who is the Guildleader?</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
The Guildleader is Qest T. Silverclaw: Timetwister Extraordinaire.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Who are the Officers of the guild?</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
<br>
All full members in good standing have the option to wear the Officer tag.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Why are you all officers?</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
<br>
It is our opinion that our general membership tends to be more mature than most other guilds leaders so why not?<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>How do you distribute loot?</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
<br>
It is distributed as the membership sees fit, preferably without a lotto, on a Need Before Greed basis with the exception of items listed on player’s “want lists.”  This works well because of the high level of maturity of the membership.  Other factors may be taken into account, but that’s generally how it goes.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>What faction are you on?</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
<br>
The guild does not require any faction, nor does it require any member to change any faction.  That said, when we kill in the Temple of Veeshan, we generally increase our Giant faction and get Kael Quest armor.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>What equipment/keys/flags do I need?</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
<br>
We have no specific equipment requirements, but our average applicant has an Enduring Breath item, just about all their spells through level 62, and a Plane of Valor Flag.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>What levels do you accept?</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
<br>
We will consider applications from characters as low as 50th level, though the basic requirement is level 60.  Applicants below level 60 must be sponsored and be really stellar players.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Can I get help with…?</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
<br>
Yes.  If there is something in the game you desire above all else, we will help you.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>How can I get in?</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
<br>
Create a new Topic in the <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub46.ezboard.com/fzerosum75695frm12" target="top">Applicants Forum</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>What information should I put in my application?</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
<br>
There is no standardized application, however some suggestions of things to include are:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Why don't you tell us what you find fun in EQ? What bothers you? What the biggest raid you were ever on was like. What your goals are. What guild(s) you've been a part of and what you like/didn't like about them. What's your favorite group make-up? What do you hope to find in Zero Sum?</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
The above are just suggestions. We'll consider your application even if it does not follow the suggestions above.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>What happened to my application after I posted it?</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
<br>
It was moved to a private area for consideration.  Please contact Qest for your status after 48 hours.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>What about my alt?</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
<br>
You may designate your characters however you wish and play whichever one suits your fancy at the time.  Playing more than one character will cause you to be considered for less loot overall since you are participating in fewer events with any particular character.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>What classes do you seek?</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
<br>
We are currently accepting applications for all classes.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Are there any other requirements?</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
<br>
You must have all expansions including Kunark, Velious, Luclin, Power, and Ykesha.  You must have a fully functional ezboard account which is free.<br>
You must have maps installed.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>What are some of your biggest kills as a guild?</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
<br>
Dain Frostreaver IV, Klandicar, Sontalak, Lcea Katta, BoT Tower Bosses, PoP mini-bosses, Cazic-Thule v2, Sleeper's Tomb <p><!--EZCODE HR START--><hr /><!--EZCODE HR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Qest T. Silverclaw, Timetwister Extraordinaire<br>
